  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110180893464\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110180893464\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&#65279;항생제 남용으로 인한 건강의 문제가 많이 언급됩니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그럼에도 불구하고 아이를 부모는 항생제를 두고 항상 갈등에 빠지게 됩니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">우리 아이가 빨리 낫기를 바라는 마음에 항생제를 쓰고 싶은 유혹이 여전히 강하기 때문일 것입니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">항생제를 쓰면 좋지 않다는건 알고 있지만, 그만큼 쓰고 싶은 마음도 있는거죠. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">식약처에서 항생제 사용에 대한 안내 자료를 만들었기에 </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">여기에 소개해 봅니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131205_81/isuhani_1386219866609L8mID_JPEG/1.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"388\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 523px\" id=\"20131205_81/isuhani_1386219866609L8mID_JPEG/1.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A74B0318')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131205_81/isuhani_1386219866609L8mID_JPEG/1.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131205_224/isuhani_1386219866868TvpzG_JPEG/2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"387\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 521px\" id=\"20131205_224/isuhani_1386219866868TvpzG_JPEG/2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A74B0318')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131205_224/isuhani_1386219866868TvpzG_JPEG/2.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131205_247/isuhani_1386219867212DCc5a_JPEG/3.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"387\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 521px\" id=\"20131205_247/isuhani_1386219867212DCc5a_JPEG/3.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A74B0318')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131205_247/isuhani_1386219867212DCc5a_JPEG/3.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131205_241/isuhani_1386219867492WjdYc_JPEG/4.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"355\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 478px\" id=\"20131205_241/isuhani_1386219867492WjdYc_JPEG/4.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A74B0318')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131205_241/isuhani_1386219867492WjdYc_JPEG/4.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131205_195/isuhani_1386219867717v7lgo_JPEG/5.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"387\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 522px\" id=\"20131205_195/isuhani_1386219867717v7lgo_JPEG/5.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A74B0318')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131205_195/isuhani_1386219867717v7lgo_JPEG/5.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.